subsection.def:
food (食物)
                                does not include food for special medical purposes;
                                        (L.N. 130 of 2024)

food additive group (食物添加劑組) means a group of food
                                additives specified in column 1 of Schedule 1A;
                                        (L.N. 130 of 2024)

permitted antioxidant (准許抗氧化劑) means a food additive that—(a)is specified—(i)in column 2 of Schedule 1,
                                                  whether or not by reference to a food additive
                                                  group of which the food additive is a
                                                  participating additive; or(ii)in column 2 of Schedule 1B;
                                                  and(b)functions primarily as an antioxidant;
                                                  (L.N. 130 of 2024)

permitted preservative (准許防腐劑) means a food additive that—(a)is specified—(i)in column 2 of Schedule 1,
                                                  whether or not by reference to a food additive
                                                  group of which the food additive is a
                                                  participating additive; or(ii)in column 2 of Schedule 1B;
                                                  and(b)functions primarily as a preservative;
                                                  (L.N. 130 of 2024)

sell
                                        (售賣) includes offer or
                                expose for sale or have in possession for sale;

paragraph.content:
the combined level of butylated hydroxyanisole, butylated
                                    hydroxytoluene, propyl gallate, octyl gallate and dodecyl
                                    gallate does not exceed 240 mg/kg;

the combined level of butylated hydroxyanisole, butylated
                                    hydroxytoluene, propyl gallate, octyl gallate and dodecyl
                                    gallate does not exceed 300 mg/kg;
